{"TopicId":175820,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"Mod to have flags turned off by default","CreatedByName":"doggonemess","CreatedById":160106,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-11T08:57:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"doggonemess","CreatedById":160106,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-11T08:57:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a mod to have flags turned off by default? I always think it\u0027s annoying having to remove them when I build new craft. If I want a flag, it\u0027s going to be on one part, and most of the time I don\u0027t want them there anyway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf it doesn\u0027t exist, I\u0027d like to make it, if I new where to start.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"notquitehalf","CreatedById":166554,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-11T10:31:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/177223-messy-recipe/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022177223\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/177223-messy-recipe/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Messy Recipe\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Wrote this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E// Turn off flag decals by default\n// Author: Messy Recipe\n\n@PART[*]:HAS[@MODULE[FlagDecal]]:FINAL\n{\n\t@MODULE[FlagDecal]\n\t{\n\t\t%flagDisplayed = false\n\t}\n}\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are a heap of other cool module manager patches in this thread:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8763647580\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/139980-130-community-database-of-module-manager-patches-for-stock-ksp/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:225px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}